    "description": "Action RPG Roguelike. Evolve your abilities and push yourself through a procedurally generated level. <br>Think hard about your choices, itemize well and use your skills to reach the end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826880/extras/0ee8e3844b2b088b5de325b93709a99f.poster.avif?t=1670304930\" width=400 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826880/extras/0ee8e3844b2b088b5de325b93709a99f.webm?t=1670304930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826880/extras/0ee8e3844b2b088b5de325b93709a99f.mp4?t=1670304930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Start with a few basic abilities and fight your way through increasingly difficult enemies to upgrade your abilities and loot gear.<br>Pick your favourite ability combinations and create unique builds with items that you find along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826880/extras/cfabc0dc3f04bbcc1bfe15d3b227a37e.poster.avif?t=1670304930\" width=400 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826880/extras/cfabc0dc3f04bbcc1bfe15d3b227a37e.webm?t=1670304930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826880/extras/cfabc0dc3f04bbcc1bfe15d3b227a37e.mp4?t=1670304930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your upgradable abilities consist of:<br>* Spell (default attack)<br>* Dash<br>* AOE Nova<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826880/extras/2e749d56bede8fbf1682370078557b51.poster.avif?t=1670304930\" width=400 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826880/extras/2e749d56bede8fbf1682370078557b51.webm?t=1670304930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826880/extras/2e749d56bede8fbf1682370078557b51.mp4?t=1670304930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What type of player do you want to be? Will you dash into a big group of mobs, praying that your raw damage will save you? Do you build movement speed and choose crowd control upgrades to strategically kite mobs around the room? <br><br>It's up to you, there are no wrong ways to play the game.<br>Well... Perhaps a few.",
